error.message:
Cannot reflectively invoke constructor 'public java.lang.Object()'. To allow this operation, add the following to the 'reflection' section of 'reachability-metadata.json' and rebuild the native image:

    {
      "type": "java.lang.Object",
      "methods": [
        {
          "name": "<init>",
          "parameterTypes": []
        }
      ]
    }

The 'reachability-metadata.json' file should be located in 'META-INF/native-image/<group-id>/<artifact-id>/' of your project. For further help, see https://www.graalvm.org/latest/reference-manual/native-image/metadata/#reflection

